{
  "page": "Addam Hightower",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For others with the same name, see <a href=\"/index.php/Addam\" title=\"Addam\">Addam</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\"><img alt=\"House Hightower.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/50px-House_Hightower.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/75px-House_Hightower.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/100px-House_Hightower.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Addam Hightower</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\"><img alt=\"House Hightower.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/50px-House_Hightower.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/75px-House_Hightower.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/100px-House_Hightower.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Beacon_of_the_South\" title=\"Beacon of the South\">Beacon of the South</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Defender_of_Oldtown\" title=\"Defender of Oldtown\">Defender of Oldtown</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Defender_of_the_Citadel\" title=\"Defender of the Citadel\">Defender of the Citadel</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Oldtown\" title=\"Lord of Oldtown\">Lord of Oldtown</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Hightower\" title=\"Lord of the Hightower\">Lord of the Hightower</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Port\" title=\"Lord of the Port\">Lord of the Port</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Voice_of_Oldtown\" title=\"Voice of Oldtown\">Voice of Oldtown</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">House Hightower</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\nIn or before <a href=\"/index.php/Years_before_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_22_Before_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years before Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">22&#160;BC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Calculation_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Calculation-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/10_AC\" title=\"10 AC\">10</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_23_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">23&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Calculation_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Calculation-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Manfred_Hightower_(Aegon%27s_Conquest)\" title=\"Manfred Hightower (Aegon&#39;s Conquest)\">Manfred Hightower</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nUnknown</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Manfred_Hightower_(son_of_Addam)\" title=\"Manfred Hightower (son of Addam)\">Manfred Hightower</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-son_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-son-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Patrice_Hightower\" title=\"Patrice Hightower\">Patrice Hightower</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Addam Hightower</b> was Lord of the <a href=\"/index.php/Hightower\" title=\"Hightower\">Hightower</a> and head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">House Hightower</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Addam_Hightower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/10_AC\" title=\"10 AC\">10&#160;AC</a>, during the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Dornish_War\" title=\"First Dornish War\">First Dornish War</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fowler\" title=\"House Fowler\">Fowler</a> led an army into the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>. By the time the <a href=\"/index.php/Marcher_lords\" title=\"Marcher lords\">marcher lords</a> realized the threat, a dozen villages had already been burned and <a href=\"/index.php/Nightsong\" title=\"Nightsong\">Nightsong</a> had been captured. When word reached <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>, Addam was sent by his father with a strong force to retake the castle. When Addam arrived at Nightsong, Lord Fowler had already put the castle to the torch and the garrison to the sword, taking Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Caron\" title=\"House Caron\">Caron</a>, his wife, and their children back to Dorne as captives. Worse, while Addam had marched from Oldtown to Nightsong, a second Dornish force had come down to attack the city, burning fields, farms and villages nearby, killing Addam's younger brother <a href=\"/index.php/Garmon_Hightower\" title=\"Garmon Hightower\">Garmon</a> in battle. Instead of pursuing the Dornish host that had taken the Carons, Addam returned to Oldtown to relieve the city, only to find the Dornish host gone upon their arrival.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Soon after Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Manfred_Hightower_(Aegon%27s_Conquest)\" title=\"Manfred Hightower (Aegon&#39;s Conquest)\">Manfred Hightower</a> died, and Addam succeeded his father as the Lord of the High Tower.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Addam was eventually succeeded by his son,<sup id=\"cite_ref-son_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-son-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Manfred_Hightower_(son_of_Addam)\" title=\"Manfred Hightower (son of Addam)\">Manfred</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Addam_Hightower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Manfred_Hightower_(Aegon%27s_Conquest)\" title=\"Manfred Hightower (Aegon&#39;s Conquest)\">Manfred</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />wife</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr>\n<tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span><